FBIS3-49991 "dreeu014_k_94010" FBIS-EEU-94-014 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Jan 1994 CROATIA Foreign Minister Issues Statement on Hurd Visit LD2001213894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 2100 GMT 20 Jan 94 LD2001213894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Text] This is a statement by our [Croatian] Foreign Minister [Mate] Granic after a brief meeting with [British Foreign Secretary] Douglas Hurd: [Begin Granic recording] We talked about the situation in Bosnia-Herzegovina. We talked about the latest round of talks in Geneva. I briefed Mr. Hurd on the results of the Geneva conference, especially on the importance of the joint declaration on the normalization of interstate relations and the settlement of the UN Protected Areas, which we signed with the FRY. [end recording]
